      • single

        public static Validations.ValidationBuilder single()
        Returns:
        A builder for a single validation rule. Typically used to provide a validation rule within another validation rule.

      • builder

        public static Validations.ValidationsBuilder builder()
        Returns:
        A builder for a set of validation rules. The builder allows validation rules to be chained together, and then finalized with build().
